rror during search for WM movement type (000 Q )"&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;The error is triggered at this point in the BAPI because it cannot find a line because the P_RBLVS field is empty.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="sonnyBarros_3-1718267659891.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/122990iA64E8CA37F4D0D9C/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="sonnyBarros_3-1718267659891.png" alt="sonnyBarros_3-1718267659891.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;My table is filled if the field is not empty.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="sonnyBarros_4-1718267889466.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/122992i32CD27677DD48889/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="sonnyBarros_4-1718267889466.png" alt="sonnyBarros_4-1718267889466.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I don't understand why the field is empty.&lt;BR /&gt;Can you help me?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Thanks in advance&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
