    <updated>2024-06-14T15:53:01.911000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>vishnucta</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/6604</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Team,&lt;BR /&gt;I am following below blogs for Outbound communication to access OData service in S4 on-premise. Ended up with "403" forbidden error.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;(Additional step 3 of adding &lt;SPAN&gt;SAP_COM_0200&amp;nbsp;into a communication Arrangement.&amp;nbsp;SAP_COM_0200 is not available in steampunk instance&lt;/SPAN&gt;)&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/enterprise-resource-planning-blogs-by-sap/outbound-communication-from-cloud-to-on-premise-in-s-4hana-cloud/ba-p/13540015" target="_blank"&gt;https://community.sap.com/t5/enterprise-resource-planning-blogs-by-sap/outbound-communication-from-cloud-to-on-premise-in-s-4hana-cloud/ba-p/13540015&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;in Step 4 of below tutorial(S4 public is used in tutorial),&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;A href="https://developers.sap.com/tutorials/abap-environment-business-partner-outbound-call.html#0664684a-34cb-4c03-87cd-f72ffec8e773" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://developers.sap.com/tutorials/abap-environment-business-partner-outbound-call.html#0664684a-34cb-4c03-87cd-f72ffec8e773&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I have added my virtual host and made 'Cloud Connector' switch on with an optional SCC ID given.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="vishnucta_0-1718372958997.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/123790i96B72D3BCDC573F5/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="vishnucta_0-1718372958997.png" alt="vishnucta_0-1718372958997.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;But after all this configuration , the check fails in Communication Arrangement&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="vishnucta_2-1718373057174.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/123794i9EE7E93C7310C67A/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="vishnucta_2-1718373057174.png" alt="vishnucta_2-1718373057174.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Error as follows:&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="vishnucta_3-1718373154435.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/123795i66757A6F7ED577F4/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="vishnucta_3-1718373154435.png" alt="vishnucta_3-1718373154435.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Can anyone point our what i am missing!!!&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;Below my SAP CC config&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="vishnucta_0-1718374384324.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/123799i2535358D1B485992/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="vishnucta_0-1718374384324.png" alt="vishnucta_0-1718374384324.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Communication scenario:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="vishnucta_1-1718374463484.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/123800iB7222CF18C20FAD5/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="vishnucta_1-1718374463484.png" alt="vishnucta_1-1718374463484.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;Best regards,&lt;BR /&gt;Vishnu&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/2108"&gt;@julieplummer20&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/821396"&gt;@ariannamussobarcucci&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/4296"&gt;@FrankJentsch&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Any help appreciated.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
